title: >>> CUPID is PISSED
body_text:
The results are in ladies and gentlemen. The official poster has been selected for February 11th:
Congratulations to Dan Spengeman who created the Valentine's Day design (#3). He won by a large margin with over half of the votes.
Lenny Herrera finished in both second and also tied for third with both of his designs, #1 and #4, respectively. John Tronolone tied with Lenny for third place with #2.
Final Results:
#3 ... 53% (Design by Dan Spengeman)
#1 ... 17% (Design by Lenny Herrera)
#2 ... 12% (Design by John Tronolone)
#4 ... 12% (Design by Lenny Herrera)
#5 ... 3% (Design by Kathryn Nogueira)
#6 ... 3% (Design by Diana DiBuccio)
The poster has been chosen by you the people. What a way to kick off DODGEBALL TWENTY-SIX. The weather reports are calling for a large amount of snow, so if that is the case, dodgeball will witness the first ever "Snow Ball I".
